{"tid":1818076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［分化撚/反港獨速入] 什麼是自由？何謂平等政治？","createTime":"2020-01-09T15:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T02:44:02.000Z","uid":11055,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a06bd975afb3da4ac6f6f7cd38ab5f9a18fc9046","tid":1818076,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4T4O4Dm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4T4O4Dm.jpg&h=d5e007e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分化撚一定無讀過政政，口講自由，但係完全唔尊重自由。 節錄下學術論文畀你哋睇啦：<br />\n<br />\n【自由主義論文】<br />\n<br />\n「政府及社會應該寬容人們的選擇──無論這些選擇在他人眼中，是多麼的離經叛道和難以接受。」──周保松《自由主義、寬容與虛無主義》。<br />\n<br />\n周保松係呢篇論文，以洛克（John Locke）、密爾（J.S. Mill），同埋羅爾斯（John Rawls），闡述出自由主義嘅觀點，同埋嘗試論證自由主義係有道德基礎，嚟反駁虛無主義者。呢篇論文最尾，周保松仲嘗試回應埋「寬容悖論」（the paradox of toleration）。<br />\n<br />\n呢篇論文而家已經收錄咗喺周保松嘅《自由人的平等政治》（新版），各位可以借或者買呢本書，嚟好好咁讀下呢篇論文。<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n請善用起底功能。 @hongkongindex 經常發表分化言論，對上一次係分化上水勇武手足，今次到分化獨派手足。🤷&zwj;♂ @hongkongindex 好唔尊重獨派手足言論自由， 請勿再扮大台。 🙏<br />\n<br />\n#轉載 #自由主義 #寬容"},{"pid":"4b489d85315b7996b5834a45715ce1070a0518f0","tid":1818076,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cdabe4d32da196e66ceac054760aaccaa467131","tid":1818076,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db1d320a7d7b6d9faea3176512eeab78dffba176","tid":1818076,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe6551c7883fca3e1c0fd5fef9aa3ed8091779e","tid":1818076,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb25ed38f64cb02cc0f5999e5cfad3ab179432c","tid":1818076,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":